1. To add Cucumber plugin in Eclipse
	(Help -> Install new Software --> http://cucumber.github.com/cucumber-eclipse/update-site)

2. To navigate to StepDefinition Class from feature file 
	(Single Click on feature file line and press F3 or Right Click --> Find Step )
	
3.  To fix the warning message in feature file (Does not have a matching glue)
	(Right click project -> Configure -> Convert to Java Cucumber Project)

4. To format the feature contents
	(Right Click --> Pretty Format)

	
5. Running Cucumber Scripts from Command Line
	mvn test
	
6. Running specific feature file only
	mvn test -Dcucumber.options="features/login/login.feature"		
	